42 (b) No later than December 31, 2025, and at least once every five years thereafter, each
43 local school system shall provide each current employee with the notice required in
44 paragraph (1) of subsection (a) of this Code section.
45 (c) Beginning July 1, 2025, and continuing thereafter, each local school system shall notify
46 each employee at or near the time of such employee's separation whether social security
47 taxes were withheld from his or her pay during any part of his or her employment."
48 SECTION 3.
49 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025.
50 SECTION 4.
51 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
